               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">How Supplied</content>
                     <br/>Kolorz Sixty Second Fluoride Foam is available in 4.4 oz. (125g) can and do not contain chlorofluorocarbon propellant.<br/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20110311"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section>
               <id root="a0d06276-7354-44c1-bc2e-55cf4b0d750f"/>
               <code code="34067-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="INDICATIONS &amp; USAGE SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">INDICATIONS</content>
                     <br/>For the topical application of fluoride to aid in the protection against dental caries. Shake can thoroughly for at least 30 seconds before each use. Hold can completely upside down to dispense. See package insert for dosage information.</paragraph>
